	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64341129"><p>The error before MCAS activated was that the autopilot nosed the plane down due to relying on a single malfunctioning sensor, and they were simultaneously warned that the plane was flying too fast and that the plane was flying too slow. The apparent existence of two opposing warning conditions should have disengaged any automatic actions of any kind as the system was clearly hopelessly confused.</p></div>
